### Get basket by user
GET {{Basket_HostAddress}}/basket/johndoe
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Update (create or update) basket
POST {{Basket_HostAddress}}/basket/
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "userName": "johndoe",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "productName": "Product 1",
      "price": 0,
      "quantity": 2,
      "color": "red"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Delete basket by user
DELETE {{Basket_HostAddress}}/basket/johndoe
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Keycloak access token (password grant)
POST {{Keycloak_Host}}/realms/{{Keycloak_Realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Accept: application/json

grant_type=password&client_id={{Keycloak_ClientId}}&username={{Keycloak_Username}}&password={{Keycloak_Password}}&scope=email

###